#  Al3+, Ga3+, Y3+, Pr3+, Nd3+, Gd3+, Eu3+, Tb3+, Yb3+, La3+ 
#  and i refers to the oxidation or charge on the cation core.
#  These values can be obtained by returning to the periodic
#  table and clicking on "O" then "Bush 1994".
#
